Output docs/assets/demo.gif

Require ./bin/agents

Set Margin 20
Set MarginFill "#6B50FF"
Set BorderRadius 10
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set TypingSpeed 75ms

Hide
Type "./bin/agents"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Show

Sleep 2s
Type "Hello, I want to build a Python ADK agent."
Sleep 1s
Enter

Sleep 3s
Type "Can you generate the agent.yaml for me?"
Sleep 1s
Enter

Sleep 3s
